name: sfchronicle
text:
Temperatures in downtown San Francisco are expected to reach 91 on Sunday and 99 on Monday, as hot, dry, smoky air descends on the Bay Area over the weekend.

name: sfchronicle
text:
Four-time cable car bell ringing champion Leonard Oats performs on the turntable at Powell and Market streets in San Francisco. Muni is rolling a cable car onto the Powell turntable three days a week for photo ops and for a scene of normalcy. 

Read more: https://t.co/87il3zs2fP https://t.co/w1Mci6JUqV
